nodes.text: Intel Agent 438432 was an individual who worked as a spy. At some point during the reign of the Galactic Empire, the agent held a confidential meeting with Sub-Prefect Helkson Vall of Kalandis IV. During the meeting, Vall recounted to the agent the story of the demise of the Imperial official Matagorn at the hands of the Srrors'tok bounty hunter Tyionsis Cex.
